UBONGA umyeni ongasekho emhlabeni umfelokazi waKwaZulu-Natal ohlabane ngesamba sikaR56 million weLotto ebese kuphele iminyaka eyizama kodwa lutho inhlanhla.  Owesifazane osekuphele unyaka ashonelwa ngumyeni, uhlabane ngoR56 million emuva kokuthi edlale ngo-R7.50 kuphela eMeerensee Dried Fruits And Nuts, eRichards Bay.Â  AbeThuba bathi umfelokazi oseyinikiwe imali, wayedlale iPowerBall Jackpot kaR112 million yangoMeyi 4 kanti uzohlala, wangabe esazibheka izinombolo eziwinile. "Bengilokhu ngidlala izinombolo ezifanayo selokhu kwaqala iPowerBall eNingizimu Afrika. Bengingazi ukuthi ngiwinile kwaze kuba ngibona udaba obelushicilelwe ephephandabeni lomphakathi, kuthiwa kufuneka owine uR56 million wePowerBall. Yingaleso sikhathi engibheke khona ithikithi lami.  Ngathuka ngibona ukuthi ngiwinile nokuwusuku olufanayo nokwashona ngalo umyeni wami nyakenye,"kusho umfelokazi. Ephetha umfelokazi uthe ziningi izinto asezihlelele le mali, ezingezogcina ngokusiza yena kuphela kodwa zizothuthukisa nempilo yomndeni wakhe. "Sengivele ngibusiswe ngayo yonke into engiyidingayo. Ngizosebenzisa lo mhlomulo ngithengele indodana yami nonkosikazi wayo umuzi nemoto. Enye ngizoyisebenzisa ukunakekela umama wami, ngisize nomngani wami onenkinga yemali njengamanje, bese ngiyilondoloza enye imali,"kusho umfelokazi. Isikhulu esiphezulu seThuba, uCharmaine Mabuza, sithe bayamhalalisela kakhulu owesifazane ngokuhlabana ngalesi samba semali. Uveze nokuthi abantu abahlabana kwiPowerBall basuke beqhamuka ezindaweni eziningi ezahlukene eNingizimu Afrika kanjalo nangaphansi kwezimo ezingefani. Lokhu uthe kuyinhloso yabo ukuthi iLotto ikwazi ukudlalwa kalula yibona bonke abantu, okuyinto abayibona yenzeka kusukela ngo-2015 bethola ilayisensi yokusabalala kuzwelonke. Uphethe ngokuthi welulekiwe  owesifazane ohlabanile njengoba kwenziwa kusukela kubantu abahlabane ngoR50 000 kuya phezulu.